{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idaa13c8db-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s3224"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3224"},"text":"§ 3224.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Director: participation, concurrence, and approval in cost estimation","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"The Director of Cost Assessment and Program Evaluation may—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idaa13c8dc-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s3224/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" participate in the discussion of any discrepancies between an independent cost estimate and the cost estimate of a military department or Defense Agency for a major defense acquisition program or major subprogram of the Department of Defense;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idaa13c8dd-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s3224/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" comment on deficiencies in the methodology or execution of any cost estimate or cost analysis developed by a military department or Defense Agency for a major defense acquisition program or major subprogram;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idaa13c8de-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s3224/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" concur in the choice of a cost estimate within the baseline description or any other cost estimate (including the discussion of risk for any such cost estimate) for use at any event specified in ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t10/s3221/b/6"},"text":"section 3221(b)(6) of this title","children":[],"tail":"; and"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idaa13c8df-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s3224/4"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"4"},"text":"(4)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" participate in the consideration of any decision to request authorization of a multiyear procurement contract for a major defense acquisition program or major subprogram.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idaa13c8e0-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":"(Added and amended ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/283/dA/tXVIII/s1812/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 116–283, div. A, title XVIII, § 1812(a)","children":[],"tail":", (e), "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2021-01-01"},"text":"Jan. 1, 2021","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/134/4174"},"text":"134 Stat. 4174","children":[],"tail":", 4175.)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idaa13c8e1-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idaa13c8e2-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"codification","id":"idaa13c8e3-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Codification","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The text of subsec. (d) of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t10/s2334"},"text":"section 2334 of this title","children":[],"tail":", which was transferred to this section and amended by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/283/s1812/e"},"text":"Pub. L. 116–283,